S.FORM: ryax sa tay 20 nqu tay 12, Mohamed Ould Abdel Aziz , squliq na sezi'. (minhtuw sa kawas tay 1956) mrhuw Mauritania ta' misuw hya' ga Mohamed Ould Abdel Aziz, aring ryax tay 5 squ byacing tay 8 sa kawas 2009 lga, musa' spazyang balay ms'rux kya la. mintzyuwaw nya Mohamed Ould Abdel Aziz Van der Bellen sa kawas 2005, t'aring mtzyuwaw zyuwaw na sezi.
